[01/12/2018 15:32:53] <font color="#ffffff">(Jess Glynne "Hold My Head")</font>
[01/12/2018 15:36:59] <font color="#ffffff">(Música)</font>
[01/12/2018 15:37:01] <font color="#00ff00">"Saber y Ganar",</font>
